  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, there isn't publicly available information regarding the ownership of \"mp4mania.\" It's possible that \"mp4mania\" refers to a smaller or less widely known website, service, or platform. To obtain accurate and up-to-date information about the ownership, you can try the following approaches:\n\n1. **Visit the Official Website:**\n   - Check the website's \"About Us,\" \"Contact,\" or \"Legal\" sections, where companies often provide information about their ownership or management team.\n\n2. **WHOIS Lookup:**\n   - Use a WHOIS lookup service (such as [whois.icann.org](https://whois.icann.org/) or [whois.net](https://www.whois.net/)) to find registration details for the domain `mp4mania`. This can provide information about the domain registrant, administrative contacts, and sometimes the organization behind the site.\n\n3. **Business Directories and Databases:**\n   - Search business directories or databases like LinkedIn, Crunchbase, or local business registries to see if \"mp4mania\" is listed and if ownership details are provided.\n\n4. **Contact Directly:**\n   - If contact information is available on the website, consider reaching out directly to inquire about ownership or organizational details.\n\n5. **Search for News Articles or Press Releases:**\n   - Sometimes ownership changes or relevant information are covered in news outlets or official press releases. A web search might yield relevant results.\n\nIf \"mp4mania\" is a newly established entity or operates under a different primary name, information might not be widely available yet. Ensuring you're accessing official and reputable sources will provide the most accurate information.",
